Package spas.taglib.handlers

Contains custom tag classes for handling forms.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActivateCourse
    Handles activation form for a course.
    Calendar
    Tries to save/update user's iCalendar file.
    ChangeCourseGroup
    Handles form for changing group for a course.
    ChangeEmail
    Tries to change user's email, whether it works or not, prints out accordingly.
    ChangePword
    Tries to change user's password, whether it works or not, prints out accordingly.
    CompleteCourse
    Handles completion form for a course.
    DeactivateCourse
    Handles deactivation form for a course.
    LogIn
    Tries to log user in.
    LogOut
    Tries to log user out of the system.
    NewPword
    Tries to email user his new password and save it to file.
    Register
    Tries to register user into the database.
    RemoveCourse
    Handles removal form for a course.
    RemoveUser
    Tries to remove user.
